2521 {
2522 typedef uint16_t Type;
2523 enum _enumType : uint16_t
2524 {
2525 NONE = 0x0000,
2526 RCV_1_DATA_VALID = 0x0001,
2527 RCV_2_DATA_VALID = 0x0002,
2528 ANTENNA_OFFSETS_VALID = 0x0004,
2529 ALL = 0x0007,
2530 };
2531 uint16_t value = NONE;
2532
2533 DualAntennaStatusFlags() : value(NONE) {}
2534 DualAntennaStatusFlags(int val) : value((uint16_t)val) {}
2535 operator uint16_t() const { return value; }
2536 DualAntennaStatusFlags& operator=(uint16_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
2537 DualAntennaStatusFlags& operator=(int val) { value = uint16_t(val); return *this; }
2538 DualAntennaStatusFlags& operator|=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
2539 DualAntennaStatusFlags& operator&=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
2540
2541 bool rcv1DataValid() const { return (value & RCV_1_DATA_VALID) > 0; }
2542 void rcv1DataValid(bool val) { value &= ~RCV_1_DATA_VALID; if(val) value |= RCV_1_DATA_VALID; }
2543 bool rcv2DataValid() const { return (value & RCV_2_DATA_VALID) > 0; }
2544 void rcv2DataValid(bool val) { value &= ~RCV_2_DATA_VALID; if(val) value |= RCV_2_DATA_VALID; }
2545 bool antennaOffsetsValid() const { return (value & ANTENNA_OFFSETS_VALID) > 0; }
2546 void antennaOffsetsValid(bool val) { value &= ~ANTENNA_OFFSETS_VALID; if(val) value |= ANTENNA_OFFSETS_VALID; }
2547 bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
2548 void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
